params.sqlcmd: "select " +" to_char(SYS_COST_CTRL.\\"CURRENT_YEAR\\") as \\"CURRENT_YEAR\\", " +" to_char(SYS_COST_CTRL.\\"CURRENT_MONTH\\") as \\"CURRENT_MONTH\\", " +" to_char(SYS_COST_CTRL.\\"TERM\\") as \\"TERM\\", " +" to_char(SYS_COST_CTRL.\\"HALF_TERM_TYP\\") as \\"HALF_TERM_TYP\\", " +" to_char(SYS_COST_CTRL.\\"START_MONTH\\") as \\"START_MONTH\\", " +" SYS_COST_CTRL.\\"ORG_CD\\" as \\"ORG_CD\\", " +" M_ORG.\\"ORG_NAME\\" as \\"ORG_NAME\\", " +" to_char(SYS_COST_CTRL.\\"PC_FLG\\") as \\"PC_FLG\\", " +" to_char(SYS_COST_CTRL.\\"M_CS_PROC_PRIORITY_TYP\\") as \\"M_CS_PROC_PRIORITY_TYP\\", " +" to_char(SYS_COST_CTRL.\\"M_CS_PROC_PERIOD\\") as \\"M_CS_PROC_PERIOD\\", " +" to_char(SYS_COST_CTRL.\\"M_PROC_COST_PRIORITY_TYP\\") as \\"M_PROC_COST_PRIORITY_TYP\\", " +" to_char(SYS_COST_CTRL.\\"M_PROC_COST_PERIOD\\") as \\"M_PROC_COST_PERIOD\\", " +" to_char(SYS_COST_CTRL.\\"M_CS_PUCH_PRIORITY_TYP\\") as \\"M_CS_PUCH_PRIORITY_TYP\\", " +" to_char(SYS_COST_CTRL.\\"M_CS_PUCH_PERIOD\\") as \\"M_CS_PUCH_PERIOD\\", " +" to_char(SYS_COST_CTRL.\\"CS_MAST_IF_PERIOD\\") as \\"CS_MAST_IF_PERIOD\\", " +" to_char(SYS_COST_CTRL.\\"CS_CALC_TRN_PERIOD\\") as \\"CS_CALC_TRN_PERIOD\\", " +" to_char(SYS_COST_CTRL.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\") as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" " +"from " +" SYS_COST_CTRL, " +" M_ORG " +"where " +" M_ORG.COMPANY_CD(+) = SYS_COST_CTRL.COMPANY_CD " +" and M_ORG.ORG_CD(+) = SYS_COST_CTRL.ORG_CD " +" and SYS_COST_CTRL.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ?"

"update " +" SYS_COST_CTRL " +"set " +" \\"CURRENT_YEAR\\" = to_number(?), " +" \\"CURRENT_MONTH\\" = to_number(?), " +" \\"TERM\\" = to_number(?), " +" \\"HALF_TERM_TYP\\" = to_number(?), " +" \\"START_MONTH\\" = to_number(?), " +" \\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"ORG_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"PC_FLG\\" = to_number(?), " +" \\"M_CS_PROC_PRIORITY_TYP\\" = to_number(?), " +" \\"M_CS_PROC_PERIOD\\" = to_number(?), " +" \\"M_PROC_COST_PRIORITY_TYP\\" = to_number(?), " +" \\"M_PROC_COST_PERIOD\\" = to_number(?), " +" \\"M_CS_PUCH_PRIORITY_TYP\\" = to_number(?), " +" \\"M_CS_PUCH_PERIOD\\" = to_number(?), " +" \\"CS_MAST_IF_PERIOD\\" = to_number(?), " +" \\"CS_CALC_TRN_PERIOD\\" = to_number(?) " +"where " +" SYS_COST_CTRL.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" M_ORG.\\"ORG_NAME\\" as \\"ORG_NAME\\" " +"from " +" M_ORG " +"where " +" M_ORG.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ORG.\\"ORG_CD\\" = ?"
